      &lt;/activation&gt;
      &lt;repositories&gt;
        &lt;!--This has to be declared here in order to allow child modules to be able to fetch older parent POMs.--&gt;
        &lt;repository&gt;
          &lt;id&gt;cloud-artifacts&lt;/id&gt;
          &lt;url&gt;artifactregistry://...&lt;/url&gt; &lt;!--use actual full URL here--&gt;
          &lt;releases&gt;
